I know, let me share some shocking, sometimes the administration doesn't tell us the truth.

659
01:00:22,884 --> 01:00:38,293
So you realize that even though you rushed the vote, even though we realized we got information about finances no more than a few days prior to that, that there were still multiple layoffs and we lost many, many teachers.

660
01:00:39,493 --> 01:00:42,515
So that was a lie.

