01:00:46,117 --> 01:00:51,520
We could have waited and move this out a week after and got the information that all of our citizens wanted.

663
01:00:52,799 --> 01:00:58,381
not the 200 people that were here that found babysitters, but everybody, that's our responsibility.

664
01:00:59,361 --> 01:01:00,182
But we didn't do that.

665
01:01:02,122 --> 01:01:06,864
You made a choice to service the people that service you.

666
01:01:08,564 --> 01:01:09,925
And that's blatant.

667
01:01:11,165 --> 01:01:18,028
You talk about, Councilor Seng talks about just picking up the phone, call the departments.

668
01:01:19,708 --> 01:01:21,929
I don't trust the departments.

